{"tid":624997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【石棺藏屍】「小草」出庭作供 獲控方豁免起訴","createTime":"2018-04-11T05:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T06:19:23.000Z","uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"406ad2bbd6aa4c99369182007c65046e60b2aa5e","tid":624997,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180411/large/1523420990_dad9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180411%2Flarge%2F1523420990_dad9.jpg&h=e757c31c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前年3月在荃灣工廈Dan6發生的石棺藏屍案，控方傳召案中主要證人「小草」何菱瑜出庭作證。案發時她與3名被告在涉案單位同居。她甫宣誓作供，法官便解釋指，她獲律政司給予一份「免予起訴書」，即她承諾作供期間必須給予全面和詳細證供。法官指本案是一宗謀殺案，發生於2016年3月4日，解釋若她給予全面和真確的證供，則律政司不會就本案的謀殺罪、或本案引申的任何控罪向她提出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n惟法官指出若「小草」在宣誓下作假證供、或作任何虛假陳述、或所作證供互相矛盾，此豁免起訴書則視為無效，「小草」表示明白。<br />\n<br />\n法官並吩咐「小草」放心，若作供期間有任何冒犯問題，法官會打斷發問，「小草」表示明白。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180411/58059165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58059165&d=a3%2FA6laLgyZZ0mbNJ%2FLrwgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=efd4422a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58059165&h=b779ca6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180411/58059165</a>"},{"pid":"cd9a885aadf1ade5624ea5e80f3e241224267267","tid":624997,"uid":37708,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"推到佢做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043a14ad1b974805feeeabfb9e0d99e5aaecbcaf","tid":624997,"uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"香港已死"},{"pid":"17e2ea28fa48f4976f36a27153ec222e352dd81c","tid":624997,"uid":59898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc239cd4a9e0c3d3326bad820a72b4ab0325de7","tid":624997,"uid":173002,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"明顯係謀殺案共犯，不過最大問題係宜家香港當權者帶頭衝擊法治，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一位市民係台灣講一句說話本身不違法，特首同官媒都可以連日上綱上線，再睇睇政府對係台灣殺人既反應，涉及律政司、警隊到知法犯法，政府更想不了了之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362487c35e2cca65f90fc0ae02ca9ddfa72d8488","tid":624997,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:17:23.000Z","msg":"知情不報都可以無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11aa4643ff112cd8ab60cc45c950c5a1f056e8a","tid":624997,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"362487c35e2cca65f90fc0ae02ca9ddfa72d8488","tid":624997,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:17:23.000Z","msg":"知情不報都可以無罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"真係唔係咁易做到, 幾時出書教人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75c31d0aed520bc0581c70bc65d2a996e0a58db","tid":624997,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"女權真係大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}